impl DiGraph {
    /// Compute PageRank scores.
    /// Returns array of scores in node index order.
    pub fn pagerank(&self, damping: f64, max_iterations: u32) -> Vec<f64> {
        let config = PageRankConfig {
            damping,
            max_iterations,
            tolerance: 1e-6,
        };
        algorithms::pagerank::pagerank(self, &config)
    }
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] PageRank converges for all test cases
- [ ] Handles dangling nodes correctly
- [ ] Handles cycles correctly
- [ ] Results match Go implementation within tolerance
- [ ] Performance: <10ms for 1000 nodes
- [ ] Unit tests pass

